Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak punya apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.55,0:00:18.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hidup dengan mengikuti arus.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.41,0:00:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan jati diri yang aku kira\Nberhasil kudapatkan, ternyata hanya ilusi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.98,0:00:26.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruto, aku tidak bisa melihat gairahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.09,0:00:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permainanmu tidak menyentuh hatiku.\NSama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar, Tuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.88,0:02:26.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tunggu aku!\N- Tuan, itu berbahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tertangkap...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manajer, kamu baik-baik saja?\NApi di kepala...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.63,0:02:39.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Duh, bikin kaget saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata tidak padam.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak yang lincah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini, sih, terlalu lincah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ups.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kucing peliharaanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.79,0:03:02.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.51,0:03:06.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin ia sedang kesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daripada dikejar, lebih baik diam dan tunggu,\Nia yang akan menghampirimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saja. Aku juga memelihara kucing...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo? Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang di Hotel Tasogare.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.68,0:03:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berada dalam kondisi tidak tahu\Nsudah mati atau masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pantas saja aku tidak tahu namaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah menginap di hotel ini
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan berhasil mengingat semua,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda akan mengetahui tujuan akhir Anda.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tujuan akhir itu akhirat, atau...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Aku mengandalkan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman sama sepertiku, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana ini...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kucing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, tunggu aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.31,0:04:29.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu, karena datang bersama,\Nkukira ini kucing peliharaan tamu kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kucing ini tidak membiarkan\Nanak itu menyentuhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kucingnya juga\Ntidak berusaha menjauh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.48,0:04:40.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia selalu memperhatikan dari tempat agak jauh.\NKenapa bisa begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu setuju, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.35,0:04:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, Tsukahara Neko\Nsedang bersama seekor kucing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya ini bukan sesuatu yang lucu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.05,0:04:54.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manajer, apa aku yang akan melayani\Ntamu baru kita?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke. Tolong, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.21,0:05:00.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Karena kita sesama\Ntidak tahu apa-apa, mau berteman?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Aku mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.48,0:05:06.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, aku akan mengantar Anda ke kamar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik. Aku mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebelah sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, kita juga kembali ke kamar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kucingnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku yang menggendong kucing ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.21,0:05:31.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa, aku merasa tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.88,0:05:35.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku orang\Nyang menggemari musik...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musik jaz, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.11,0:05:40.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Itu tas apa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saksofon, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa saksofon ini milikku?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika berada di kamar ini, mungkin saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku boleh mainkan di dalam kamar?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar, namamu...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Atori. Tuan bisa mainkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Atori.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.31,0:06:31.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya aku hampir ingat sesuatu,\Nternyata tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, tunggu dulu di sini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda menyukai luar angkasa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.54,0:06:53.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Kalau sudah besar,\Naku ingin menjadi seorang astronaut.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mimpi yang hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pantas saja kepalanya seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.93,0:07:02.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti, orang tua Anda\Nyang membelikan mainan roket itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mamaku usil.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benci Mama!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walah, ada tamu yang tidak biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kamu masih terlalu kecil\Nuntuk datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh? Kelihatannya kalian benci aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Datang lagi saat sudah dewasa nanti, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.18,0:07:42.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ralat. Kalau ada di hotel ini,\Nbelum tentu kamu bisa tumbuh dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.38,0:07:45.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Osoto, abaikan saja anak ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jutek banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.95,0:07:51.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Konon, anak kecil dan hewan\Nbisa menebak watak asli seseorang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saja dia menyadari sesuatu\Nsaat melihatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan berkata seolah aku\Nyang tamu biasa ini orang berbahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu memang orang berbahaya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, lewat sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.53,0:08:04.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati, masih panas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, sedang bersedih, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.28,0:08:22.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang menganggur, mau main bersama?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau main apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebetulan ada sesuatu yang cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh kumainkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tahu lagu ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu! "Menginjak Kucing"!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kasihan kalau kucingnya terinjak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya. Kalau lagu ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau mainkan bersama?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga bisa mainkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bermain musik itu seru, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti seorang kakek dan cucunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.00,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku ikut senang mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah seperti pentas anak-anak, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.68,0:09:34.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria itu seorang musikus, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu karena bisa bermain piano juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang kelas atas memang beda.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan. Maaf menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini, kamu makan di bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa Ruri menghindariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai mengantuk, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akhiri saja sampai sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan, mari kembali ke kamar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Kak Atori?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menu makan siang anak-anak!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, kamu terlihat bersemangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.21,0:10:47.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jarang-jarang aku membuat menu itu,\Nternyata menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga mau makan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau makanan sisa,\Nada di sebelah sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Atori juga mau?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atori?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih makanannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.61,0:11:06.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Atori bersikap aneh sejak kemarin.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak membuatnya marah\Nkarena mengacaukan pekerjaan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.98,0:11:13.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, nasi omelet buatan Mama itu\Nenak sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin coba.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama pasti akan buatkan\Nkalau Paman mampir ke rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama ada di mana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.08,0:11:38.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski pernah bilang benci,\Ndia sebenarnya ingin bertemu ibunya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saja dia benar-benar benci.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruri?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.31,0:11:59.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jarang-jarang aku bisa\Nmelihat Kak Atori melamun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Neko.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang tidak enak badan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau mungkin sedang galau?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau, aku bisa jadi teman curhat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Neko, kamu ingat ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, piringan hitam yang pernah dipinjam.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.88,0:12:30.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beliau adalah pemain saksofon\Njaz kelas dunia, Ogawa Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria berkepala piringan hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.91,0:12:36.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Kak Atori bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.25,0:12:42.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak dulu, sebagai ganti bisa melakukan apa saja,\Naku tidak punya hal yang membuatku terobsesi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa seperti inilah hidup,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan tidak pernah merasa kurang puas.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang pamer, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.85,0:12:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu,\Naku mendengar permainan saksofonnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terpesona oleh permainannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.18,0:13:02.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suara permainannya\Nterdengar seperti datang dari jiwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa,\N"Andai aku juga bisa bermain seperti itu..."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, aku pergi ke Amerika\Nuntuk belajar dengan serius.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku tidak punya apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya,\Naku menyerah dan pulang ke Jepang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.48,0:13:29.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu,\Naku tidak bisa membuang piringan hitam ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.11,0:13:33.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau memang suka, ya sudah.\NItu saja sudah cukup, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.88,0:13:38.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku, jika itu untuk idola, hidup di tengah\Napi atau laut pun aku akan bahagia!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, kalau sekarang,\Nmungkin aku sudah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar khas Neko.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.48,0:13:47.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selagi bisa bertemu idola,\Nkenapa tidak ngobrol lebih banyak?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beberapa tahun ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,kondisi jantung Tuan Ogawa memburuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.05,0:13:59.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin beliau sudah...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.55,0:14:08.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, membantu tamu\Nmengingat adalah kewajiban kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Ogawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.78,0:14:32.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku memainkan lagu ini\Ndi konser terakhirku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku terlalu asyik\Nmemainkan lagu ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.61,0:14:39.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidak sadar kalau aku sudah meninggal.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.28,0:14:45.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awalnya, aku memulai profesi ini\Nuntuk mencari nafkah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.19,0:14:50.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, makin aku sering tampil,\Nmusik pun menjadi alasan untuk hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat menikmatinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.14,0:14:55.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, pasti bohong\Nkalau aku bilang tidak punya penyesalan,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku hidup dengan bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:04.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak punya hal\Nyang bisa membuatku seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya hal yang aku suka,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku cepat menyerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.78,0:15:16.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat muda dulu,\Naku juga sering merasakan kegagalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.61,0:15:21.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu masih muda, bisa jadi apa saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.25,0:15:31.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak itu juga masih sangat muda.\NSemoga dia bisa pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon, berhenti membuat kamar berantakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah, kalau seperti ini terus...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tertangkap!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak tidak apa-apa? Sesak?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya menghirup debu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.84,0:15:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat batuk,\NMama selalu mengelus punggungku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, aku akan merasa lebih baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu berarti...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obat asma?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.14,0:16:11.57,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Nama Anda adalah Watanabe Shouta?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pakai ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda sudah ingat semua?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.15,0:17:08.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama melarangku memegang hewan\Nkarena asmaku akan kambuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu "Meong".\NKarena berbunyi "Meong, meong".
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat membawa pulang Meong, Mama...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh.\NBagaimana kalau asmanya makin parah?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shouta!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benci Mama.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.91,0:17:43.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat asmaku sembuh dan lebih kuat,\Naku akan menjadi seorang astronaut.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Konon, Bumi terlihat biru dari luar angkasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.64,0:17:51.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matahari dan bintang juga ada di dekat kita.\NPasti menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu, aku akan bawa Meong juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meong? Meong!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Meong.\NAku tidak sempat menolongmu. Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Geli.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia ingin bilang kalau Tuan\Ntidak perlu cemas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.50,0:18:24.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semenjak datang ke sini,\Nia menghindari Tuan Shouta
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.25,0:18:26.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,supaya Tuan tidak merasa sesak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meong.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.51,0:18:34.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, ibu Tuan Shouta\Nhanya mencemaskan kondisi Tuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.91,0:18:35.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.98,0:18:40.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama selalu ada di sampingku\Nsetiap aku sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shouta, Shouta.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Shouta?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon, Shouta. Buka matamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama sudah memanggilku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo. Kamu juga sudah ingat semuanya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Aku akan pulang ke rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya. Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.51,0:19:19.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia tidak akan kesepian,\Naku akan bawa ia bersamaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada tamu yang check out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.44,0:19:27.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman, tolong manjakan Meong, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.11,0:19:34.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lakukanlah banyak hal menyenangkan\Nsaat tiba di rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.68,0:19:40.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga kamu hidup dengan baik,\Npenuh tawa, dan berhasil mewujudkan mimpi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya. Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.78,0:20:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya tenang... Ehem. Jadi sepi, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.31,0:20:04.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, kita juga harus berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.78,0:20:12.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu mau mendengarkan\Npermainan terakhirku?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.28,0:20:38.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pernah terkena serangan jantung\Ndi sebuah hotel,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan ada seorang concierge\Nyang menyelamatkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.05,0:20:48.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena ia segera memberi pertolongan,\Naku bisa bermain musik sedikit lebih lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Atori.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permainan yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini milik Tuan Ogawa, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak menghilang bersama pemiliknya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.85,0:21:30.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terkadang, ada barang tamu yang tertinggal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.71,0:21:33.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biasanya, aku akan mengoleksi\Nbarang-barang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.11,0:21:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya Atori yang harus menerima ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Na-Namun,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sudah...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Ogawa terlihat sangat puas.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Atori juga senang bisa\Nbertemu dengannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nterima saja kenang-kenangan ini.
